cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with real-time image-based localization, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The method also involves feature extraction and matching, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates the method in large indoor and outdoor scenes, which could fall under computer graphics (cs.GR).
